  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ 425°F/ Gas 7</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into <strong>chunky chips</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chunky chips</strong> to a baking tray with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\n<p>Trim the <strong>Brussels sprouts</strong> and chop them in half</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>chopped sprouts</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong> and blitz for 30 secs or until finely shredded</span></p>\n<p>Tip: Don't have a food processor? Slice them finely instead!</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>dried cranberries </strong>to a small bowl, cover them with <strong>boiled water </strong>and set aside to soak</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>shredded sprouts</strong> to a colander and pour the remaining<strong> boiled water</strong> all over them until bright green and wilted, then set aside to steam dry</p>\n<p>Peel and finely slice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced onion</strong> to the pot and cook for 10-15 min, stirring frequently, or until golden and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Whilst the onions are cooking, line a baking tray with <strong>baking paper</strong></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>venison &amp; pork burgers</strong> to the tray and put the tray in the oven for 12-14 min or until the burgers are cooked through (no pink meat!)</span></p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the burgers are cooking, drain the <strong>soaked cranberries </strong>and chop them finely </p>\n<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped cranberries</strong> and <strong>shredded sprouts</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>mayonnaise</strong>, <strong>Dijon</strong> <strong>mustard, chopped garlic </strong>(don't like raw garlic? Go easy!) and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> </p>\n<p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>sprout &amp; cranberry slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Once the burgers are cooked, slice the<strong> mini</strong> <strong>camembert<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half as if you were cutting a burger bun, so you are left with 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> thinner pieces</span></p>\n<p>Tip: Run your knife under hot water to stop it sticking to the cheese!</p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Top each <strong>venison &amp; pork burger</strong> with a <strong>camembert half</strong> and add the <strong>brioche rolls</strong> to the other side of the tray</span></p>\n<p>Return the tray to the oven for 2-3 min or until the cheese has melted and the brioche is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Once the onions have caramelised, add the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> to the onion and cook for 1-2 min further or until the vinegar has been absorbed and the onions are sticky – these are your <strong>balsamic onions</strong></span></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Fill each <strong>brioche roll</strong> with the<strong> balsamic onions</strong>, a <strong>venison &amp; pork camembert burger</strong> and a dollop of <strong>cranberry sauce</strong></span></p>\n<p>Serve the<strong> sprout &amp; cranberry slaw</strong> and<strong> chunky chips </strong>to the side</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
      "media": {
        "images": []
      }
    }
  ],
